79
00:04:16,199 --> 00:04:16,959
Grant me a divorce!

80
00:04:17,199 --> 00:04:18,839
Absolutely not!

81
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,560
Xueying,

82
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:25,639
Liang's career is flourishing,

83
00:04:26,199 --> 00:04:28,120
and you've just received
your noble title.

84
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:30,680
A divorce now

85
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:32,759
would shame us all!

86
00:04:33,199 --> 00:04:33,759
Grandmother,

87
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:37,120
he openly cavorts with courtesans.

88
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,519
Such behavior

89
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:41,079
shows utter disregard for me

90
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:43,079
and brings disgrace to our family!

91
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:46,480
Your rumors with Lu Junxing
spread like wildfire,

92
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,160
yet you dare blame me?

93
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,279
Grandmother,

94
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:52,680
the whole city knows

95
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:54,639
he slandered me with the Prince Heir

96
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:57,160
to hide his own misdeeds!

97
00:04:57,519 --> 00:04:59,040
I cannot swallow this humiliation!

98
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,000
Please grant the divorce!

99
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,639
Liang has gone too far.

100
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:11,560
Perhaps,

101
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,959
give him another chance?

102
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:16,279
I'll punish him severely.

103
00:05:27,199 --> 00:05:27,920
Lu Liang,

104
00:05:28,519 --> 00:05:32,560
