107
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,079
At court,

108
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:47,879
talented men are as common as carp.

109
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,519
Why should you

110
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:52,519
rise three ranks in one year?

111
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,160
Your Highness,

112
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,519
my achievements

113
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,480
are entirely due to your patronage.

114
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,319
Then remember

115
00:06:04,879 --> 00:06:06,839
you promised me

116
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,600
in exchange for my support,

117
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:12,160
you will offer your wife
to me for pleasure.

118
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,240
Yes.

119
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,600
Where is she?

120
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:18,360
I mean Jiang Xueying.

121
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:27,079
Your Highness,

122
00:06:28,079 --> 00:06:30,759
her behavior has drastically
changed recently.

123
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:32,560
She wants to divorce me.

124
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,000
She and Lu Junxing have

125
00:06:34,639 --> 00:06:35,040
close....

126
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,240
I don't need explanations

127
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,480
but the person.

128
00:06:38,399 --> 00:06:38,920
Understand?

129
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,560
I have little patience left.

130
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,120
Absolutely.

131
00:07:01,279 --> 00:07:03,439
Lady Yu'er, you're finally awake.

132
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:09,720
How long was I asleep?

133
00:07:12,199 --> 00:07:13,199
Where's Jiang Xueying?

134
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:16,199
Here. It's delicious.

135
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,480
Jiang Xueying!

136
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,160
Stop right there!

137
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,240
Didn't you want a divorce?

138
00:07:30,519 --> 00:07:32,120
Come. Let's discuss this privately.

139
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,240
What's so secretive

140
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,279
to go inside?

141
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,639
Speak here.

142
00:07:42,639 --> 00:07:43,920
Agree to one condition,

143
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:46,000
and I'll sign the letter of divorce.

144
00:07:47,199 --> 00:07:48,240
It won't work.

145
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,279
I made myself clear.

146
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:53,160
I demand a divorce agreement.

147
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:56,800
Don't go too far.

148
00:07:57,199 --> 00:08:00,439
Lu Liang, you're in no position

149
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,879
to bargain.

150
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,360
Fine.

151
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:07,000
