152
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,720
Accompany me to a banquet tomorrow

153
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:12,160
and behave cooperatively.

154
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,079
After the banquet,

155
00:08:13,079 --> 00:08:14,600
I'll sign the divorce agreement.

156
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:15,720
No tricks.

157
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:18,399
