at Prince Ning's Mansion?

159
00:08:22,959 --> 00:08:23,319
You...

160
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:26,160
How did you know?

161
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,439
The banquet is just a cover.

162
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:31,000
You actually want to offer me
to Prince Ning,

163
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,679
climbing the social ladder, right?

164
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:34,000
Stop.

165
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:35,000
Are you insane?

166
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:35,639
Shut up!

167
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,279
I know you too well.

168
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:45,039
Your so-called talents

169
00:08:45,519 --> 00:08:47,200
were merely laughable pretenses

170
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,240
with my help.

171
00:08:49,919 --> 00:08:51,879
You put on a facade in front of others,

172
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:54,320
but actually you're a gambling,
lustful wretch.

173
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,759
What can you do

174
00:08:56,759 --> 00:08:58,080
besides wallow in vices?

175
00:08:59,000 --> 00:08:59,879
You little fool!

176
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:01,080
How dare you!

177
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,360
Everything you have now

178
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:07,440
was gained by clinging to Prince Ning.

179
00:09:08,039 --> 00:09:09,960
