180
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:11,480
Just to please your master,

181
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,279
you'd even send your own wife

182
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,840
to his bed.

183
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,919
