186
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:34,559
Let's use their same tactic.

187
00:09:34,919 --> 00:09:35,960
Just capture Lu Liang

188
00:09:36,399 --> 00:09:37,320
and force him to sign

189
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,320
the divorce agreement.

190
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,039
If he refuses,

191
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,559
kill him outright.

192
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:43,519
So,

193
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,720
after being reborn once,

194
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,279
you've become quite impatient?

195
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:53,120
You're my wife,

196
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,360
yet you bear the title
of Lu Liang's wife.

197
00:09:55,720 --> 00:09:56,759
Seeing you humiliated,

198
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,840
how can I accept this?

199
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,639
How can I stay calm?

200
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:03,879
He's just a clown,

201
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,840
not worth fearing.

202
00:10:06,559 --> 00:10:08,120
But now it appears

203
00:10:08,679 --> 00:10:10,240
Prince Ning is making his move.

204
00:10:10,679 --> 00:10:12,159
In last life, he used dirty trick

205
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:13,879
to possess you.

206
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,720
Now he might use Lu Liang again

207
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:19,039
or find other excuses to harm you.

208
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,360
You must finalize the divorce quickly.

209
00:10:30,759 --> 00:10:32,440
When this is over,

210
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:36,879
I desperately need rest.

211
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:39,879
Then we'll gallop across grasslands,

212
00:10:40,879 --> 00:10:42,000
and watch sunrises in peace.

213
00:10:43,039 --> 00:10:44,120
I'll accompany you wherever

214
00:10:44,639 --> 00:10:45,440
you want to go.

215
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,519
(It can't delay any longer.)

216
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:53,039
