219
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,960
You're skilled in this area.

220
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,360
Please audit them.

221
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,399
How dare you!

222
00:11:02,399 --> 00:11:03,440
We're not even married.

223
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:04,840
Now you want me to help you?

224
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,559
Sooner or later.

225
00:11:18,639 --> 00:11:21,360
Jiang Xueying, that fool!

226
00:11:22,159 --> 00:11:25,000
After receiving her title,
how did she change so drastically?

227
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:28,519
How did she discover my plan?

228
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,440
Isn't this

229
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,279
the Princess Consort Junxing divorced?

230
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,519
Since I've come here,

231
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:43,320
I'll get straight to the point.

232
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,759
