at home until recently.

233
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,440
Only now did I learn

234
00:11:48,879 --> 00:11:50,240
the Prince Heir divorced me

235
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,639
because of Jiang Xueying.

236
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:54,159
If I don't take revenge,

237
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,399
I'll never find peace.

238
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,679
So you want my help?

239
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,759
You all keep coming

240
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,200
wanting to deal with Jiang Xueying.

241
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,919
Do you know how cunning that woman is?

242
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:12,960
