247
00:12:32,679 --> 00:12:34,559
Don't hold back, Master Liang.

248
00:12:35,320 --> 00:12:37,159
I'm just a discarded wife now.

249
00:12:37,679 --> 00:12:39,559
No threat to you.

250
00:12:44,639 --> 00:12:45,840
I plan to

251
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:49,360
gift her to a nobleman.

252
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,159
Deliver her to another's bed.

253
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:59,639
Quite ruthless, Master Liang.

254
00:13:05,919 --> 00:13:07,960
The lady of rank acts so superior,

255
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,080
looking down on everyone.

256
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:11,440
Drag her from the clouds into the mud.

257
00:13:12,080 --> 00:13:13,240
