266
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,919
Now that I've been divorced
by the Prince Heir,

267
00:13:40,399 --> 00:13:41,559
and disowned by my family.

268
00:13:42,159 --> 00:13:43,279
I'm desperate.

269
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:44,840
I need a powerful patron

270
00:13:45,600 --> 00:13:47,120
and secure my future.

271
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:51,759
Hmm.

272
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,519
With your looks,

273
00:13:55,879 --> 00:13:58,240
