274
00:13:59,279 --> 00:14:00,080
Okay.

275
00:14:00,919 --> 00:14:01,879
Deal.

276
00:14:14,559 --> 00:14:15,136
Grandmother,

277
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,919
after marrying Lu Liang,

278
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:17,919
Xueying suffered greatly.

279
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:19,720
I can't bear her misery.

280
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:22,120
Please grant

281
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,639
her divorce request.

282
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,399
Have you lost your mind?

283
00:14:27,519 --> 00:14:28,679
She's your cousin's wife!

284
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,320
If you truly care for her,

285
00:14:31,639 --> 00:14:34,039
don't ruin her reputation.

286
00:14:34,720 --> 00:14:37,080
Which is more important,
her reputation or her happiness?

287
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:39,600
Should we force Xueying

288
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,600
to suffer

289
00:14:42,519 --> 00:14:44,480
silently forever

290
00:14:44,480 --> 00:14:45,639
to preserve our reputation?

291
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:46,840
How dare you!

292
00:14:47,080 --> 00:14:48,600
As the Prince Heir,

293
00:14:48,919 --> 00:14:49,919
you dare propose

294
00:14:49,919 --> 00:14:52,279
this disgrace to our family!

295
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:54,519
If you grant Xueying's divorce,

296
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,720
I'll renounce my title.

297
00:14:57,519 --> 00:14:58,799
What did you say?

298
00:14:59,240 --> 00:15:00,639
I'll surrender my inheritance

299
00:15:00,639 --> 00:15:02,759
to another clan member.

300
00:15:03,679 --> 00:15:04,759
In this lifetime,

301
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,879
I want only Xueying.

302
00:15:07,720 --> 00:15:09,120
You're a fool!

303
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,919
Without your title,

304
00:15:13,120 --> 00:15:14,799
possessing nothing,

305
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:18,320
you think she'd stay?

306
00:15:18,639 --> 00:15:19,480
She would.

307
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:22,080
We've faced life and death together.

308
00:15:22,799 --> 00:15:24,000
Nothing

309
00:15:24,679 --> 00:15:26,240
will change that.

310
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,159
Never imagined

311
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:30,039
you could be so devoted.

312
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,559
Too bad this devotion

313
00:15:31,960 --> 00:15:33,960
is directed at my wife!

314
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:39,159
You don't deserve her!

315
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,559
I hold official rank.

316
00:15:41,600 --> 00:15:43,759
But you only hold
the title of Prince Heir.

317
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:45,279
Do you think you deserve it?

318
00:15:45,279 --> 00:15:46,919
Enough of your words.

319
00:15:48,519 --> 00:15:50,120
You two cousins

320
00:15:50,799 --> 00:15:53,240
have actually fought
like this over a woman.

321
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,200
You're letting outsiders

322
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,039
laugh at us!

323
00:15:57,759 --> 00:15:59,519
Your Ladyship speaks wisely.

324
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,519
As a descendant of the Lu family,

325
00:16:01,519 --> 00:16:03,039
I should prioritize the greater good.

326
00:16:03,759 --> 00:16:06,080
Since Junxing is so determined,

327
00:16:06,919 --> 00:16:09,399
I'm willing to divorce
Jiang Xueying to fulfill

328
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:10,320
their union.

329
00:16:14,159 --> 00:16:15,120
However...

330
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:16,960
Go on speaking!

331
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:20,159
I have one condition.

332
00:16:31,456 --> 00:16:35,320
♪Traces of intertwined fate♪

333
00:16:35,584 --> 00:16:39,480
♪Silent jade carves the foreshadowing♪

334
00:16:39,648 --> 00:16:42,760
♪Among all living beings, only you♪

335
00:16:43,264 --> 00:16:48,864
♪I'd willingly drown♪

336
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:55,160
♪Lantern in hand, fingers entwined♪

337
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:59,440
♪You light my life, day and night♪

338
00:16:59,872 --> 00:17:07,640
♪Into your arms, through life and death♪

339
00:17:08,032 --> 00:17:11,840
♪I gaze at the moon and stars afar♪

340
00:17:11,936 --> 00:17:16,160
♪May your longing linger forever♪

341
00:17:16,224 --> 00:17:23,560
♪In dreams and beyond, I'll be with you♪
